OL,3,CCalls for better overtime pay for
OL,4,CLondon doctors as 32,000 shifts got
OL,5,Cunfilled
OL,7,FMore than 32,000 shifts, meant to have
OL,8,Fbeen staffed by doctors in hospitals
OL,9,Facross the capital, were left unfilled
OL,10,Fover a six-month period in 2024,
OL,11,Faccording to the British Medical
OL,12,FAssociation (BMA).
OL,14,FFreedom of Information (FOI) requests
OL,15,Fsubmitted by the BMA revealed that
OL,16,Facross 23 London trusts at least
OL,17,F32,576 shifts were offered to doctors
OL,18,Fbut not filled.
