OL,3,CCalls for better overtime pay for
OL,4,CLondon doctors as 32,000 shifts got
OL,5,Cunfilled
OL,7,FThe BMA has warned that the scale of
OL,8,Funfilled shifts is having a
OL,9,F"detrimental impact" on patient care
OL,10,Fand means remaining doctors are left
OL,11,Fworking "increasingly understaffed and
OL,12,Fchallenging" shifts.
OL,14,FIt claims low pay is to blame for the
OL,15,Flack of doctors willing to work extra
OL,16,Fshifts, describing rates as "not
OL,17,Fcompetitive enough and often worse
OL,18,Fthan those offered outside of the
OL,19,Fcapital".
