OL,5,Cunfilled
OL,7,FThe union said it had received
OL,8,Fanecdotal reports of doctors at the
OL,9,Fsame level of seniority being paid
OL,10,Fthree times the London rate for the
OL,11,Fsame shifts in other parts of the
OL,12,Fcountry.
OL,14,FIt also said members had reported
OL,15,Ftravelling out of the city to do their
OL,16,Fextra work.
