OL,5,Cunfilled
OL,7,FLondon Resident doctor Dr Shivam
OL,8,FSharma, who sent the Freedom of
OL,9,FInformation requests to all trusts in
OL,10,FLondon, said the data backs up a
OL,11,Ffeeling among doctors that London
OL,12,Fhospitals are "untenably short
OL,13,Fstaffed".
OL,15,FDr Sharma, who also co-chairs the BMA
OL,16,FNorth Thames Regional Resident
OL,17,FDoctors' Committee, added: "Every
OL,18,Fsingle one of those 32,000 unfilled
OL,19,Fshifts meant overworked doctors were
OL,20,Fleft trying to do the work of multiple
OL,21,Fmedics.
