OL,3,CCalls for better overtime pay for
OL,4,CLondon doctors as 32,000 shifts got
OL,5,Cunfilled
OL,7,F"Patients in London deserve doctors
OL,8,Fwho can give them the time and energy
OL,9,Fthey need.
OL,11,F"As doctors, we can see first-hand the
OL,12,Fimpact of huge waiting lists and
OL,13,Fovercrowded A&E departments with
OL,14,Fpatient being treated on corridors and
OL,15,Fit makes even more frustrating that
OL,16,Ftrusts in London are dragging their
OL,17,Fheels on this."
