OL,5,Cunfilled
OL,7,FThe BMA is now calling on NHS Trusts
OL,8,Fin the capital to negotiate "better
OL,9,Fand fair" rates for doctors to make
OL,10,Fextra shifts more appealing.
OL,12,F"It's only common sense that if trusts
OL,13,Fabandoned the medical rate cap and
OL,14,Fpaid these shifts more competitively,
OL,15,Fas trusts in other parts of the
OL,16,Fcountry can do, we would see fewer
OL,17,Frota gaps and better-staffed
OL,18,Fhospitals," Dr Sharma said.
