OL,7,FA spokesperson from NHS London told
OL,8,FITV News: "NHS England London's top
OL,9,Fpriority is patient safety, and we
OL,10,Fwork closely with trusts and systems
OL,11,Fcross the capital to support best
OL,12,Fpractice.
OL,14,F"On average, around 90 per cent of
OL,15,Fshifts are filled in hospitals across
OL,16,FLondon and for those that aren't,
OL,17,Fthere could be a variety of reasons
OL,18,Ffor not filling them."
