OL,7,FA spokesperson from the Department of
OL,8,FHealth and Social Care said: "The NHS
OL,9,Fworkforce has been overworked for
OL,10,Fyears, leading to staff becoming burnt
OL,11,Fout and demoralised.
OL,13,F"Our Plan for Change will ensure we
OL,14,Ftrain and provide the staff,
OL,15,Ftechnology and infrastructure the NHS
OL,16,Fneeds to care for patients across our
OL,17,Fcommunities.
